.\" Man page for vdr-newplugin

.TH vdr-newplugin 1
.SH NAME
vdr-newplugin

.SH SYNOPSIS

.B vdr-newplugin
.I <pluginname>

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B vdr-newplugin
creates a new plugin source directory from which to start implementing
a plugin for VDR.

The source directory will be created in the active working-directory.

